---
config:
theme: neo-dark
---
sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant R as Resident
    participant API as FastAPI
    participant D as DormSystem
    participant C as LeaseContract
    participant I as Invoice

    Note over R,API: API Pay Invoice

    R->>+API: POST /pay(invoice_id)
    API->>+D: pay_invoice(invoice_id)

    D->>+I: get_invoice_by_id(invoice_id)
    alt invoice not found
        I-->>D: raise LookupError
        D-->>API: raise LookupError
        API-->>R: HTTP 400
    else invoice found
        I-->>-D: invoiceObj

        D->>+I: validate_for_payment()
        alt status == PAID
            I-->>D: raise ValueError
            D-->>API: raise ValueError
            API-->>R: HTTP 400
        else status == UNPAID
            I-->>-D: pass

            D->>+C: get contract by invoice_id
            alt contract not found
                C-->>D: raise LookupError
                D-->>API: raise LookupError
                API-->>R: HTTP 400
            else contract found
                C-->>-D: contractObj

                D->>I: status = PAID
                D->>C: status = ACTIVE
                D-->>-API: contractObj
                API-->>-R: contract_id, contract_status, message
            end
        end
    end